


 
 (本文部份照片提供：劉力仁）
昨天在台北， Facebook 非常低調的在台北舉行了第一次於台灣舉辦的 World Hack Day，活動的時間是一天，地點在信義區裡的克緹國際總部大樓，場地應該是台灣目前舉辦過的 Hackday裡最棒的一次，從挑高的落地窗裡可以清楚望見 101 大樓，不過中午的餐點似乎略顯不足：p

 

台灣許多知名的開發者都參與了本次的活動，活動的核心主要在介紹 Facebook 在 Social Graph 上的應用，下午才開始開發者間的競賽活動，儘管台上使用的是英文介紹，台下很貼心的提供同步口譯的服務，儘管台灣的開發者們英文很好（？），所以沒什麼能用，但是這是非常貼心且值得贊許的作法。

從現場開發者們的設備來看，Apple Macbook 已經成為國內開發者主力使用的機種選擇，乍看之下會不會也頓時以為是來到「蘋果開發者大會」呢？



晚間則是 DEMO 以及頒獎時間，最後由以下產品獲得獎項（由於官方沒有公告得獎名單，我也沒待到最後：p，所以可能會有出入，歡迎各位指正或留言產品內容）
首獎
Name: Paperclip.ioCategory: Open GraphDescription: paerclip.io is a bookmark tracking service, it track and collect urls you like on facebook, and organize them for you. We also provide search service, so you can quick find the urls you ever like.
Mobile 類獎
Name: Before Sunrise, Before Sunset, after Facebook.Category: Mobile + Open GraphDescription: Try our Social Trip Maker, there's always chance to meet new people and place, lonely planet never be lonely again.
Game 類獎
Team Name: Memory MillionaireRelevant Categories: Game/Open GraphShort Description: Let's play a quiz game about guessing who are sharing good stories with you among your friends. You can invite your friends to a group and play together :)
Open Graph 類獎
Name: but... Category: mobile Description: fun app where you can add captions to images to create comics. You can share to facebook and also rate it up on the website!
評審特別獎
Name: Ping-pongCategory: GameDescription: We designed interesting social motion sensing ping-pong game for friends.
Name: FeedManagerCategory: Open GraphDescription: There are some articles good. All we can do is click "like". However user may want to create a folder to manage them. It’s a time to add a tag to a feed and manage them, my project is to save these feeds in “folder”.
 

 

 







